Building requires the following RPMs to be installed:

BuildRequires: glib-devel, pam-devel
BuildRequires: glib-ghash
BuildRequires: flex, bison
BuildRequires: php-devel
BuildRequires: php
BuildRequires: db4-devel (for pam_abl)

NEW:
BuildRequires: flex-devel (for server!)

Use:
yum install glib-devel pam-devel glib-ghash flex bison php php-devel db4-devel flex-devel
